%Sorting the tasks list+
 To change the sort order of the list, enter the%SORT+command and (optio
 the sort fields.  Valid sort fields are CATEGORY, PRIORITY, DATE, HOURS
 STATUS.  You may enter as many of the sort fields as you wish.  If you
 sort fields, STATUS PRIORITY HOURS DATE (in that order) will be used. N
 the current sort order is always shown on the tasks list panel, and is
